      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把这三条流转加上了。DECIDE_LATER这个状态比较特殊，用户后续还能怎么操作？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DECIDE_LATER"
